SUMMARY:Love in the Club: 2000's Hip Hop & R&B Dance Party
DTSTAMP:20260622T021942Z
DTSTART:20260906T020000Z
DESCRIPTION:Doors: 9pm LOVE IN THE CLUB is the ultimate 2000s R&B and hip h
	op dance party. A night dedicated to the era of flip phones\, iconic music
	 videos\, and unforgettable club anthems. From Usher to Missy Elliott to A
	kon\, we?re bringing the most iconic club era and hits you grew up on back
